Results.ReviewText: Drinking this coffee for years and love it. In the shops looking for this coffee only but sometimes if there is non left i will take something else but this is almost the only coffee i take ;)
Results.Title: My favourite

Results.ReviewText: This is our go-to coffee when in the supermarket - it's affordable and still tastes like a premium coffee.  Smooth and luxurious, perfect for those chilly mornings when a kick-start is needed!
Results.Title: An affordable luxury coffee

Results.ReviewText: I have been a customer of Nescafe Gold Blend for years and years. I always know when I go visiting if I am not being served Gold Blend unfortunately there is not always a convenient plant pot!
Results.Title: Favourite Fantastic Blend

Results.ReviewText: I always buy gold blend and also the decaf version for my husband.  Have tried other similar brands but always come back to my old favourite which simply cannot be beaten on taste and quality.
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: From opening a new jar , don't you love that smell ☺ , to taking your first sip ,you can smell the freshness , that distinctive fresh coffee aroma teases your taste buds from start to finish.
Results.Title: great aroma

Results.ReviewText: I buy this product regularly as it has a great taste.  Although it isn't the cheapest on the market it is worth the price and is great to serve to others.   It is full of flavour  and smooth.
Results.Title: Fantastic taste

Results.ReviewText: I love coffee and am always trying out new brands and flavours. However I always have Nescafe Gold Blend next to the kettle as I always return to this as I've not found anything to match it!
Results.Title: SERIOUSLY GOOD COFFEE!

Results.ReviewText: I don't drink much coffee but when I do I like Gold Blend and iI have been buying it for many years. I like the rich taste and it is not 'bitter. The excellent adverts started it all for me.
Results.Title: as good as ever

Results.ReviewText: I recently bought the new jar of nescafe gold blend and was really impressed by the smoothness of the drink. It really is worthwhile buying the larger bottle because I enjoy drinking it more
Results.Title: Really happy with this new coffee

Results.ReviewText: As I am not an expert, this coffee is a plain one for me. I prefer the unhealthier tastier versions, which Nescafe sells also, so this is not against the brand, just not for my taste really.
Results.Title: It is an ok coffee

Results.ReviewText: I don't drink much coffee but when I do I like Gold Blend and iI have been buying it for many years. I like the rich taste but it is not 'bitter. The excellent adverts started it all for me.
Results.Title: Gold Blend - the advert started the coffee journey

Results.ReviewText: after trying this brand I have to say I really love it and buy all the time now, It has a lovely taste and I also think is a good price toI would def rec it to anyone who likes there coffee
Results.Title: Love This Coffee

Results.ReviewText: I have recently written to Nestle to express my disappointment to the changes made to my favourite coffee.  Why change a product when people enjoyed the taste and had done so for many years
Results.Title: Disappointed

Results.ReviewText: Tried different coffees but there's no getting away from it....Gold Blend is the best.  Consistently smooth, no bitter aftertaste and makes a lovely cup or mug of coffee each and every time
Results.Title: Keep coming back to it!

Results.ReviewText: Usually buy gold blend so decided to this one a try. Oh it’s really smooth and lovely. I’m the coffee drinker in the family but have to say everyone enjoyed this coffee. Well done Nescafé!!
Results.Title: Oh so smooth!

Results.ReviewText: found this coffee in the store so i thought i would try it out wow i am so glad i did it has the most smooth taste around i will only buy this coffee from now on a big thank you to nescafe.
Results.Title: fabulous coffee

Results.ReviewText: I drink many mugs of Gold Blend origonal daily and have done for some 50 years. I hate to think of the ammount consumed but would also hate to think if Nescafe Gold Blend was not available.
Results.Title: Good Coffee

Results.ReviewText: I like my coffee twice daily and gold blend hits the spot beautifully.  Whether I want it a little stronger made mostly with water, or milky as a night time treat, I am never disappointed.
Results.Title: A good smooth cup.

Results.ReviewText: Love this coffee and will always buy this, wonderful aroma and an even beautiful taste. First drink of the day, have always drunk this brand for a very long time an will continue to do so.
Results.Title: Great Taste

Results.ReviewText: Been a fan for such a long time. Can't wait to break the seal on the new jar for the delicious aroma to hit my senses and the 'ahhhh bisto' moment kicks in but in a wonderful coffee way!!
Results.Title: Amazing aroma

Results.ReviewText: Disappointed that the coffee I always have loved has changed. It now has a sediment left at the bottom of every cup. The taste has also changed very subtly and is not so smooth as it was.
Results.Title: Why change something great?

Results.ReviewText: I always used to buy Nescafe Gold and I am not sure why I stopped because once I tasted that familiar smooth flavour I remembered why it was my favourite and I will never let it go again.
Results.Title: Back to Gold

Results.ReviewText: I have tried other coffee's but always go back to Gold Blend.  I find it a lovely blend of coffee and very smooth in taste.  It is really good value against other coffees for its quality.
Results.Title: It certainly is Gold

ClientResponses.Response: It's sad to hear you're not a fan of the changes but thank you for leaving your feedback.

Results.ReviewText: I have drunk Gold Blend for years but the new taste is dreadful - as other reviewers have said the new style is bitter and tasteless and the gritty dregs at the bottom of the cup are vile
Results.Title: Dreadful new taste

Results.ReviewText:
Have used a competitors coffee for the past 6 years but saw this new launch and decided to try it.....What a revelation... 
One heaped teaspoon  Milk first...VERY IMPORTANT...Pure heaven
Results.Title: What a pleasant surprise...

Results.ReviewText:
Many years have passed, since our relationship began.
Once I was a bride, and now I am a Nan.
A marriage made in heaven, perfection guaranteed.
A golden loving cup for our anniversary.
Results.Title: Wedded Bliss

Results.ReviewText: I have always loved Nescafe Gold Blend. I drink it a home and take it into work with me to drink at breaktime. I always drink my coffee black and Nescafe Gold Blend has the richest taste.
Results.Title: Best Coffee

Results.ReviewText: This was on special offer in the Co-op so I thought I`d give it a try. What a wonderful surprise.I  have always used Gold Blend coffee but now it has a richer, smoother taste. I love it.
Results.Title: New Richer Taste

Results.ReviewText: When I visited my sister I could smell the coffee aroma before I drank it and the taste did not let it down. I had to ask what brand it was andI have now been converted to nescafe gold.
Results.Title: NESCAFE GOLD

Results.ReviewText: I always buy the Gold edition of Nescafe. Love this coffee - it is a perfect combination between smooth and strong taste at the same time. The rich aroma contributes to the great taste!
Results.Title: Perfect combination
